"question": "Evaporation takes place over the entire mass of the liquid.",
"correctAnswer": "false",
"answer": "Evaporation is a surface phenomenon — only molecules at the very top escape. Boiling occurs throughout the entire bulk.",
"source": "icse",
"teacherTip": "Evaporation is like a \"top-down\" exit.",
"examTip": "Use the term \"surface phenomenon\" for evaporation.",
