"content": "Raj try to do experiment with the gold leaf electroscope, but he forgot to connect metal foil. His friend, Sahil asked him to connect the metal foil to the earth How do soil particles bind together? Sometimes, you see a spark or hear a crackle when you take off your polyester shirt or sweater. Do you know, why?\n\n**Must know**\n• Tungsten metal is used exclusively for designing filaments of electric bulbs.\n\n**Answers for linked questions**\n• A circuit, electric current flows from positive terminal of the cell to negative terminal of the cell.\n• Electric mixer relates to 400 – 1200, 220, and 13. Air conditioner (1.5 tonnes).\n• Tungsten metal is used exclusively for designing filaments of electric bulbs.\n• Match each term with its correct description.",
